sourcesContent: import React, { useCallback, useState } from 'react'; import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux'; // DATA Files import dataNavbar from "webapp/common/data/Navbar/main-navbar-data.json"; // Components import { HeaderOne, FooterOne } from 'webapp/common'; import PageTitleWork from 'webapp/work/component/PageTitleWork'; import 'webapp/work/style/Work.css' import { getUserList } from 'webapp/users/reducer/user.reducer'; const WorkRegister = ({ tagline, title, backfont, dash, textBtn, classes }) => { const [input, setInput] = useState({ name: "", category: "", description: "" }) const dispatch = useDispatch() const inputChange = e => { setInput({ ...input, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }) } const workRegister = e => { e.preventDefault() dispatch(getUserList()) } return ( <>
